        transition-all hover:bg-green-500 hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-green-900 dark:text-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Custom Short URLs</h3>
        <p>Create short URLs and customize their text as you wish.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl shadow-md cursor-pointer 
        transition-all hover:bg-green-500 hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-green-900 dark:text-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl">
